Create a .config file in the application root dir and place the following 
lines in it:

[gmail]
username=joesmith
password=hockey
email_template=/home/jon/code/talking-alarm-clock/templates/email.template
gmail_template=/home/jon/code/talking-alarm-clock/templates/gmail.template

[weather]
#code can be found in the url when going to a city/regions weather page on
#weather.com
code=12761347
test=blah
template=/home/jon/code/talking-alarm-clock/templates/weather.template

